# Quality Gates Rules

- Treat Spotless, Checkstyle, SpotBugs, and tests as required quality gates.
- Run `mvn clean install` before considering a task complete when code was changed.
- If any plugin reports violations, fix the code or configuration in the same change.
- Do not leave the branch with known plugin violations.
